raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Good evening kitty cat
Player: Kitty cat?
Mabel: Since I don't have Ms Whiskers with me, you'll have to fill in!
Player: Meow! 😺
Mabel: Cuuute 😻
Player: Did you figure out your weekend plans?
Mabel: Oh right
Mabel: I texted Nina and she said she'd come over and pick me up tomorrow
if Story.has_flag(\"Weekend1Promise\"):
	Mabel: But omg, we have a date tomorrow
	Mabel: Remember? You promised we'd go out hehe
	Player: I remember
	Mabel: So...
	Mabel: What should we do? 🙃
	- We can go out on Sunday! [#pinkheart]
		set Story.pink_heart += 1
		set Story.mabel_trust += 1
		set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
		set Story.flag = \"SundayDate\"
		Player: We can go out on Sunday!
		Mabel: Really!?
		Mabel: Yipee 🥰
		do echo_set([\"20\"])
		Mabel: I'm doing a little happy dance omg
		Mabel: You have no idea how much I miss you 😍
		Player: I missed you too!
		do echo_clear()
	- Don't worry, we can do it another week [#distrust]
		set Story.mabel_trust -= 3
		Player: Don't worry, we can do it another week
		Mabel: But babe 🥺
		Player: Just promise you'll try and have a good time yeah?
		Mabel: I wanted to see you this weekend but okay 😣
		Mabel: Let's spend time together soon okay?
		Player: For sure!
else:
	Mabel: I wasn't sure if we were going to do anything so I said okay
	Player: Sure thing, good chance to hang out a little!
	Mabel: Yeah I think so too
Mabel: Look at me, with weekend plans now
Mabel: img: mabel/21
Player: Settling in like a pro!
Player: Where are you going btw?
Mabel: Oh uhm... 🙂
Mabel: Nina wanted to go see the opening of the college club 😬
Player: Wait really? 😂
Mabel: Yeah 🥺
Mabel: I was all like \"Yeah sure! Sounds cool!\"
Mabel: Babe HELP!!
Player: What do you want me to do!?
Mabel: What do you mean
Mabel: This was your idea!! 😭
Player: Hey, all I said was to make friends lol
Player: You could have said no to the club thing 😆
Mabel: I knoww but 🫢
Mabel: You know how I am
Mabel: I'm always scared to disappoint people
Mabel: She's coming out of her way to hang out with me and I just wanted to be nice
Player: Don't overthink it
Player: It's not as crazy as you think, a lot of people go there just to chat
Mabel: Thought: But night time is still spooky
Mabel: Okay... sure 😅
Mabel: I'll try going for just a little
Mabel: Thanks for the push babe
Mabel: I've been hiding in my shell too long
Mabel: Thought: I hope I don't regret this
Player: I'll be waiting to hear how it went
Mabel: I don't know if I'll have any good news but
Mabel: We'll see 😅
Player: No problem, complain about it to me tomorrow
Mabel: Alright then talk tomorrow 😚❤️
Player: Nighty!
do social_post(\"caleb_gameday\")
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
